System Architecture Overview
🔑 1. Authentication Layer
Sign Up (Student or Admin)

Log In (with role validation)

Redirect based on role

🧍 2. User Roles
Admin Side

View/Add/Edit/Delete Students

View Attendance & Marks

Manage Lecturers (optional later)

Student Side

View Profile

View Marks & Attendance

Edit limited info

🏛 3. Separation of Concerns (Logical Layers)
Main.java – launches the app

LoginFrame.java – login and signup GUI

User.java – base class for Student and Admin

Student.java – student data and actions

Admin.java – admin data and actions

Database.java – mock data store (later a file/db)

DashboardStudent.java – GUI for student

DashboardAdmin.java – GUI for admin

